node.text:
Greetings on this #MonkishMiércoles! Two more for the menu…

BROADCASTING LIVE - Double IPA featuring the great Nelson Sauvin hops from @freestylehops in NZ! 8.5% ABV

MONK LIGHT - Unfiltered light pilsner. Brewed with belgian pilsner malt and german hops. Lagered for 6 weeks. 3.4% ABV

CA Beer Shipping Available 
Open 12-4p To-Go Only
Open 4-9p Normal Service

node.text:
👋🏽 Starting off the week adding two beers to the menu. 

BOMB ATOMICALLY -Double Dry Hopped (DDH) Double IPA with Mosaic, Citra, and Galaxy 8.3% ABV

SECOND STACKS - Wild ale aged in oak barrels for 12 months & conditioned on spent peaches, nectarines, & apricots. Naturally carbonated and conditioned in 750ml cork and caged bottles for an additional 12 months. Lively and lovely. 6.2% ABV 

CA Beer Shipping Available 
Open 12-4p To-Go Only
Open 4-9p Normal Service

node.text:
Ending the week with one new Freshie and some Merchie. 

🏷 INVISBLE ENIGMA
Double Dry Hopped (DDH) Double IPA with Enigma and Galaxy hops. 8.6% ABV

🏷 DISTRESSED CORE TEE
A new everyday day tee featuring our bold circle logo on the chest and a new Monkish / LA design on the back. Distressed print for a softer feel.  S-3XL

🏷 PINK DOT TEE
A new throwback to our first Monkish fermenters with bold pink logo and Monkish / LA border. Both these tees are printed on our favorite soft medium-heavyweight 100% cotton tee. S-3XL

🏷 DUFFEL BAG - BLACK ON BLACK CAMO
A new black-on-black embroidered camo duffle. Heavyweight canvas featuring our classic Monkish logo on the side. One size.

(Merch currently only available at the Tasting Room)

CA Beer Shipping Available (ships out Mon 8/30)
Open 12-10p
Food: @felicecatering 🍕

node.text:
SACRED SCALES 
Double Dry Hopped (DDH) Double IPA with Riwaka and Strata 8.4% ABV

IMPRESSIONABLE
Saison aged in French oak barrels and conditioned on spent (second use) Persian mulberries. Bottle conditioned in 750ml cork and caged champagne bottles for 16 months. Delicate… and lively and lovely🍷 5.8% ABV

12-4p TO-GO SALES ONLY (walkups and curbside)
4-9p FULL SERVICE (curbside still available til 7p)

CA Beer shipping available

New canned offerings for the weekend:
